<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Happy Birthday Annaammo</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@400;600&family=Poppins:wght@300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>

<header class="hero">
  <div class="hero-content glass">
      <h1>Happy Birthday,<br>Annaammoo 🤍</h1>
      <div class="gold-line"></div>

      <p class="subtitle">A little surprise...</p>

      <p class="message">
      Every birthday deserves a gift.<br>
      This one isn't wrapped in paper.<br><br>
      It's wrapped in memories.
      </p>

      <div class="buttons">
          <a href="#story" class="btn">Open Your Gift ✨</a>
          <button id="musicBtn" class="music">♪ Press Play</button>
      </div>
  </div>

  <div class="scroll">▼ Scroll ▼</div>
</header>

<section id="story">
<h2>Some stories are written with words.<br><span>Ours was written with moments.</span></h2>

<p>
Every photograph holds a heartbeat. Every smile reminds us of a day that quietly became unforgettable.
Some memories fade with time. Others become the reason we smile years later.
This place is more than a website. It is a collection of moments that shaped us.
A journey through laughter, silence, distance, happiness and love.
Welcome to our story.
</p>

<div class="chapter">
<p class="chapter-title">CHAPTER ONE</p>
<h3>Where everything quietly began...</h3>
<p>(Here we will later add your first memory together, along with a beautiful full-screen photo.)</p>
</div>

<p class="footer">Made with countless memories ❤️</p>

</section>

<audio id="bgMusic" src="music/song.mp3"></audio>
<script src="script.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
  
